v: 1
t: "althna' ealaa allah bsfath alty kllha awsaf kmal, wbnemh alzzahirat walbatnt, aldiyniat waldnywyt, aladhi 'ansha alsmwat wal'ard wama fyhn, wakhalaq alzulumat walnwr, wdhlk bteaqb allayl walnhar. wafi hdha dlalt ealaa ezmt allah teala, wasthqaqh wahdah alebadt, fala yajuz li'ahad 'an yushrak bih ghyrh. wamae hdha alwuduh fa'iina alkafirin yswwn biallah ghyrh, wyshrkwn bh"